      Data: 87|UnityEngine.TooltipAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: During the ONE-TIME initial world generation, updateTimeBudgetMs is temporarily
        raised to this value so the (profiled ~92% idle) GPU + async readback pipeline
        can drain far more work per frame. Frame rate during the load matters much
        less than total load time. Automatically restored to updateTimeBudgetMs once
        world gen completes. Set <= updateTimeBudgetMs to disable the boost.
