      Data: 127|UnityEngine.TooltipAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: 'Minecraft-style NEAR meshing guarantee: per-frame GPU mesh-decode time
        reserved EXCLUSIVELY for chunks near the player, drained BEFORE and independently
        of the shared aggregate budget above. MC rebuilds near chunks unconditionally
        each frame (under a time budget) so a far-chunk backlog can never starve
        the chunk you''re standing on. Bounded so it can''t spike frames; lower it
        if the headset overshoots.'
    - Name: 
      Entry: 8
      Data: 
