      Data: 130|UnityEngine.TooltipAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: 'Budget per GPU worldgen step in milliseconds. THIS IS THE MAIN LOAD-LAG
        LEVER: StepChunkDataGeneration runs GPU-worldgen blit phases in a loop bounded
        by this, so a high value (the scene was 25ms) lets a single stepping call
        run many blits and blow the frame. Keep it small for smooth load.'
