      Entry: 1
      Data: "GPU-resident chunks (#2 migration, STEP 1 safety net \u2014 default
        OFF). When on, chunks outside cpuMirrorRadius drop their CPU block mirror
        after gen and rehydrate on demand from the atlas via rehydrateReceiver. Off
        = unchanged behaviour."
