    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: 'PERF TEST (default OFF): skip the greedy face-merge growth scan and
        emit one 1x1 quad per face. Tests whether the merge scan cost outweighs the
        vertex-count savings. ON = more verts, no merge scan; OFF = greedy merge
        (default).'
